{"items":[{"item_id":"0529e9d0-ffdd-4179-b42a-adbf3053efd7","item_name":"Structure","item_icon":"custom/structure.png","item_texture":"","item_skins_dir":"custom/skins/armchairs","item_icons_dir":"custom/icons/armchairs","item_entity_dir":"entities/items/pumpkin.json","item_skin":"","premium":false,"premium_users_only":false,"disable":false,"tag":"structure","itemBuilding":"{\"author\":\"\",\"category\":\"Medieval\",\"desc\":\"The Illager Tower, a defiant symbol of the Illagers' presence, stands as a stark reminder of their encroaching threat. Constructed from rough-hewn stone and topped with a menacing banner emblazoned with a skull and crossbones, the tower rises only a few stories high, but its squat, fortified structure speaks of a watchful presence. Its walls, scarred with the passage of time and battles fought, offer a glimpse into the Illagers' relentless nature. \\n\\nAtop the tower, the flagpole stands tall, its banner fluttering in the breeze. It serves as a warning to any who dare approach, a beacon for the Illagers' relentless advance. From its vantage point, the Illagers can survey the surrounding landscape, keeping watch over their domain and plotting their next move against the unsuspecting villagers below. \\n\\n(This text was generated by Gemini)\",\"download\":1593,\"file_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/0529e9d0-ffdd-4179-b42a-adbf3053efd7.mcstructure\",\"img1_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/1723838355146_1723838441.jpg\",\"img2_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/1723838355571_1723838441.jpg\",\"img3_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/1723838355818_1723838441.jpg\",\"name\":\"Illager Tower.\",\"id\":\"0529e9d0-ffdd-4179-b42a-adbf3053efd7\",\"premium\":\"false\",\"thumb_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/image_cropper_1723838055383_1723838441.jpg\",\"data\":{\"enable\":true,\"chance\":0.75,\"isGrounded\":false,\"isUnburied\":false,\"positionY\":0,\"custom