ually stunning and immersive house for those who enjoy exploring the world of Minecraft.\\n\\nPlayers can visit or create such custom houses by searching online for \\\"Fantasy Minecraft House\\\" within the game community. These resources provide inspiration and guidance on how to design their own enchanting abode in-game, ensuring that it stands out among other creations shared by fellow players.\",\"download\":3822,\"file_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/2c775870-8846-406c-aae5-57321ac0a279.mcstructure\",\"img1_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/Fantasy-Minecraft-House_2_1740473750.png\",\"img2_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/Fantasy-Minecraft-House_3_1740473750.png\",\"img3_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/Fantasy-Minecraft-House_4_1740473750.png\",\"name\":\"Fantasy Minecraft House\",\"id\":\"2c775870-8846-406c-aae5-57321ac0a279\",\"premium\":\"false\",\"thumb_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/Fantasy-Minecraft-House_1_1740473750.png\",\"data\":{\"enable\":true,\"chance\":0.75,\"isGrounded\":false,\"isUnburied\":false,\"positionY\":0,\"custom_id\":\"2c775870-8846-406c-aae5-57321ac0a279\"},\"structureFeature\":{\"uuid\":\"a601a801-d753-42b8-8d9c-6a51b356867c\",\"featureId\":\"above ground\",\"structureId\":\"a162493f-4f50-4538-ac56-e01b1e292923\",\"adjustmentRadius\":16,\"facingDirection\":\"FacingDirection.random\",\"grounded\":true,\"unburied\":true,\"blockIntersection\":false,\"blockAllowlist\":[\"minecraft:air\"]},\"featureRule\":{\"uuid\":\"f440313c-bb46-425f-a28e-87e7dffc433e\",\"ruleId\":\"Forest\",\"placesFeature\":\"\",\"conditions\":\"{\\\"placement_pass\\\":\\\"final_pass\\\",\\\"minecraft:biome_filter\\\":[{\\\"any_of\\\":[{\\\"test\\\":\\\"has_biome_tag\\\",\\\"operator\\\":\\\"==\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"birch\\\"},{\\\"test\\\":\\\"has_biome_tag\\\",\\\"operator\\\":\\\"==\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"birch_forest\\\"},{\\\"test\\\":\\\"has_biome_tag\\\",\\\"operator\\\":\\\"==\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"bee_habitat\\\"},{\\\"test\\\":\\\"has_biome_tag\\\",\\\"operator\\\":\\\"==\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"birch_forest_hills\\\"},{\\\"test\\\":\\\"has_biome_tag\\\",\\\"operator\\\":\\\"==\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"birch_forest_hills_mutated\\\"},{\\\"test\\\":\\\"has_biome_tag\\\",\\\"operator\\\":\\\"==\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"birch_forest_mutated\\\"},{\\\"test\\\":\\\"has_biome_tag\\\",\\\"operator\\\":\\\"==\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"forest\\\"},{\\\"test\\\":\\\"has_biome_tag\\\",\\\"operator\\\":\\\"==\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"forest_hills\\\"}]}]}\",\"distribution\":\"{\\\"iterations\\\":1,\\\"scatter_chance\\\":{\\\"denominator\\\":400,\\\"numerator\\\":1},\\\"x\\\":{\\\"distribution\\\":\\\"uniform\\\",\\\"extent\\\":[0,16]},\\\"y\\\":\\\"q.heightmap(v.worldx, v.worldz)\\\",\\\"z\\\":{\\\"distribution\\\":\\\"uniform\\\",\\\"extent\\\":[0,16]}}\"}}","display_name":"Structure","group_id":"root","type":"structure","create_time":"2026-04-02T13:21:49.147644"},{"item_id":"2f86c0ae-566b-43d6-8dbf-fa4904eda651","item_name":"Structure","item_icon":"custom/structure.png","item_texture":"","item_skins_dir":"custom/skins/armchairs","item_icons_dir":"custom/icons/armchairs","item_entity_dir":"entities/items/pumpkin.json","item_skin":"","premium":false,"premium_users_only":false,"disable":false,"tag":"structure","itemBuilding":"{\"author\":\"\",\"category\":\"House\",\"desc\":\"The Medieval Library is an impressive and detailed building crafted within the game of Minecraft. It features multiple levels, each accessible by wooden stairs. The architecture has a medieval aesthetic, complete with stone walls, large windows framed in wood, and decorative elements such as torches hanging from beams.\\n\\nAtop the library stands a turret-like structure that houses additional rooms or storage areas. This central tower is flanked on both sides by smaller extensions, creating an irregular but balanced appearance for the overall building. The roof of the Medieval Library consists of dark grey tiles arranged in a zigzag pattern, adding to its rustic charm.\\n\\nThe surrounding landscape features lush greenery with various plants and flowers scattered around the base of the structure. A dirt path leads up to the entrance, inviting visitors into this charming virtual world. Overall, the Medieval Library is an inviting and picturesque representation of medieval architecture within Minecraft's blocky universe.\",\"download\":4146,\"file_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/2f86c0ae-566b-43d6-8dbf-fa4904eda651.mcstructure\",\"img1_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/Medieval-Library_2_1755156838.jpg\",\"img2_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/Medieval-Library_3_1755156838.jpg\",\"img3_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/Medieval-Library_1_1755156838.jpg\",\"name\":\"Medieval Library\",\"id\":\"2f86c0ae-566b-43d6-8dbf-fa4904eda651\",\"premium\":\"false\",\"thumb_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/Medieval-Library_1_1755156838.jpg\",\"data\":{\"enable\":true,\"chance\":0.75,\"isGrounded\":false,\"isUnburied\":false,\"positionY\":0,\"custom_id\":\"2f86c0ae-566b-43d6-8dbf-fa4904eda651\"},\"structureFeature\":{\"uuid\":\"a601a801-d753-42b8-8d9c-6a51b356867c\",\"featureId\":\"above ground\",\"structureId\":\"a162493f-4f50-4538-ac56-e01b1e292923\",\"adjustmentRadius\":16,\"facingDirection\":\"FacingDirection.random\",\"grounded\":true,\"unburied\":true,\"blockIntersection\":false,\"blockAllowlist\":[\"minecraft:air\"]},\"featureRule\":{\"uuid\":\"f440313c-bb46-425f-a28e-87e7dffc433e\",\"ruleId\":\"Forest\",\"placesFeature\":\"\",\"conditions\":\"{\\\"placement_pass\\\":\\\"final_pass\\\",\\\"minecraft:biome_filter\\\":[{\\\"any_of\\\":[{\\\"test\\\":\\\"has_biome_tag\\\",\\\"operator\\\":\\\"==\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"birch\\\"},{\\\"test\\\":\\\"has_biome_tag\\\",\\\"operator\\\":\\\"==\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"birch_forest\\\"},{\\\"test\\\":\\\"has_bi