etails invite visitors into a world of fantasy. The large central room boasts an impressive staircase leading up to what appears to be a loft or upper story.\\nThe Cherry Fantasy House is surrounded by cherry blossom trees in full bloom, their branches heavy with pink petals that add a touch of whimsy and romance to the scene. This idyllic setting evokes feelings of serenity and invites players into a realm where imagination takes flight, making it an ideal location for exploring creativity within the game's virtual world.\",\"download\":6076,\"file_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/30014e49-0dca-47f3-822c-bb6ccc10660c.mcstructure\",\"img1_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/Cherry-fantasy-house_2_1761644304.JPG\",\"img2_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/Cherry-fantasy-house_3_1761644304.JPG\",\"img3_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/Cherry-fantasy-house_4_1761644304.JPG\",\"name\":\"Cherry fantasy house\",\"id\":\"30014e49-0dca-47f3-822c-bb6ccc10660c\",\"premium\":\"false\",\"thumb_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/Cherry-fantasy-house_1_1761644304.JPG\",\"data\":{\"enable\":true,\"chance\":0.75,\"isGrounded\":false,\"isUnburied\":false,\"positionY\":0,\"custom_id\":\"30014e49-0dca-47f3-822c-bb6ccc10660c\"},\"structureFeature\":{\"uuid\":\"a601a801-d753-42b8-8d9c-6a51b356867c\",\"featureId\":\"above ground\",\"structureId\":\"a162493f-4f50-4538-ac56-e01b1e292923\",\"adjustmentRadius\":16,\"facingDirection\":\"FacingDirection.random\",\"grounded\":true,\"unburied\":true,\"blockIntersection\":false,\"blockAllowlist\":[\"minecraft:air\"]},\"featureRule\":{\"uuid\":\"a457d213-ab52-4088-821e-40b1251f3144\",\"ruleId\":\"pink\",\"placesFeature\":\"\",\"conditions\":\"{\\\"placement_pass\\\":\\\"final_pass\\\",\\\"minecraft:biome_filter\\\":[{\\\"any_of\\\":[{\\\"test\\\":\\\"has_biome_tag\\\",\\\"operator\\\":\\\"==\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"cherry_grove\\\"}]}]}\",\"distribution\":\"{\\\"iterations\\\":1,\\\"scatter_chance\\\":{\\\"denominator\\\":200,\\\"numerator\\\":1},\\\"x\\\":{\\\"distribution\\\":\\\"uniform\\\",\\\"extent\\\":[0,16]},\\\"y\\\":\\\"q.heightmap(v.worldx, v.worldz)\\\",\\\"z\\\":{\\\"distribution\\\":\\\"uniform\\\",\\\"extent\\\":[0,16]}}\"}}","display_name":"Structure","group_id":"root","type":"structure","create_time":"2026-04-02T13:21:51.946615"},{"item_id":"31a56d47-5e16-4046-b4cc-d42e39cf2d73","item_name":"Structure","item_icon":"custom/structure.png","item_texture":"","item_skins_dir":"custom/skins/armchairs","item_icons_dir":"custom/icons/armchairs","item_entity_dir":"entities/items/pumpkin.json","item_skin":"","premium":false,"premium_users_only":false,"disable":false,"tag":"structure","itemBuilding":"{\"author\":\"\",\"category\":\"Temple\",\"desc\":\"## The ID RELY STRUCTURE: A Monument of Time\\n\\nThe ID RELY STRUCTURE stands as a testament to the enduring power of time. Its imposing facade, captured in this close-up, showcases intricate architectural details and a sense of timeless grandeur. At the very pinnacle of the structure, a grand clock face dominates the skyline, its hands tirelessly marking the passage of moments.\\n\\nThe weathered stonework, etched with the patina of years, hints at a rich history. Every crack and crevice tells a story of resilience and continuity, reminding us of the enduring nature of time. The clock, with its rhythmic tick-tock, serves as a constant reminder of the flow of life, urging us to appreciate every second.\\n\\nWhile the exact purpose of the ID RELY STRUCTURE remains shrouded in mystery, its imposing presence speaks to its significance. It stands as a silent sentinel, a beacon of time in an ever-changing world. This close-up invites us to pause, to reflect, and to appreciate the enduring nature of time itself. \\n\\n(This text was generated by Gemini)\",\"download\":37,\"file_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/31a56d47-5e16-4046-b4cc-d42e39cf2d73.mcstructure\",\"img1_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/1697722148008_1697722194.jpg\",\"img2_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/1697722148425_1697722194.jpg\",\"img3_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/1697722148771_1697722194.jpg\",\"name\":\"ID RELY STRUCTURE \",\"id\":\"31a56d47-5e16-4046-b4cc-d42e39cf2d73\",\"premium\":\"false\",\"thumb_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/4_1721041099.jpg\",\"data\":{\"enable\":true,\"chance\":0.75,\"isGrounded\":false,\"isUnburied\":false,\"positionY\":0,\"custom_id\":\"31a56d47-5e16-4046-b4cc-d42e39cf2d73\"},\"structureFeature\":{\"uuid\":\"393de596-d0aa-46ec-b2c2-28e9cd54224c\",\"featureId\":\"underground\",\"structureId\":\"05b14abf-d1a9-4706-a0de-381d36cf673a\",\"adjustmentRadius\":16,\"facingDirection\":\"FacingDirection.random\",\"grounded\":false,\"unburied\":false,\"blockAllowlist\":[\"minecraft:air\"]},\"featureRule\":{\"uuid\":\"cb668d0c-28ed-4434-a737-768a0b9c3c91\",\"ruleId\":\"underground\",\"placesFeature\":\"\",\"conditions\":\"{\\\"placement_pass\\\":\\\"final_pass\\\",\\\"minecraft:biome_filter\\\":[{\\\"any_of\\\":[{\\\"test\\\":\\\"has_biome_tag\\\",\\\"operator\\\":\\\"==\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"overworld\\\"},{\\\"test\\\":\\\"has_biome_tag\\\",\\\"operator\\\":\\\"==\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"overworld_generation\\\"},{\\\"test\\\":\\\"has_biome_tag\\\",\\\"operator\\\":\\\"==\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"animal\\\"},{\\\"test\\\":\\\"has_biome_tag\\\",\\\"operator\\\":\\\"==\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"monster\\\"}]}]}\",\"distribution\":\"{\\\"iterations\\\":1,\\\"scatter_chance\\\":{\\\"denominator\\\":300,\\\"numerator\\\":1},\\\"x\\\":{\\\"distribution\\\":\\\"uniform\\\",\\\"extent\\\":[0,16]},\\\"y\\\":{\\\"distribution\\\":\\\"uniform\\\",\\\"extent\\\":[11,50]},\\\"z\\\":{\\\"distribution\\\":\\\"uniform\\\",\\\"extent\\\":[0,16]}}\"}}","display_name":"Structure","group_id":"root","type":"structure","create_time":"2026-04-02T13:21:55.736162"},{"item_