rance.\\nSurrounding the structure, lush greenery flourishes, including towering trees and various plants adding to the picturesque setting. Nearby, you can find other structures like a quaint village, a bustling port town with docked ships, and enchanting castles that add depth and variety to this Minecraft landscape.\\n\\nThe church stands as an inviting sanctuary amidst the lively atmosphere of its surroundings. Whether used for worship or simply enjoyed by players, it adds character and charm to any Minecraft adventure.\",\"download\":4805,\"file_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/66754c92-33ec-4131-b44d-c0513428ee6b.mcstructure\",\"img1_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/Old-and-tiny-Church_2_1761644306.JPG\",\"img2_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/Old-and-tiny-Church_3_1761644306.JPG\",\"img3_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/Old-and-tiny-Church_1_1761644306.JPG\",\"name\":\"Old and tiny Church\",\"id\":\"66754c92-33ec-4131-b44d-c0513428ee6b\",\"premium\":\"false\",\"thumb_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/Old-and-tiny-Church_1_1761644306.JPG\",\"data\":{\"enable\":true,\"chance\":0.75,\"isGrounded\":false,\"isUnburied\":false,\"positionY\":0,\"custom_id\":\"66754c92-33ec-4131-b44d-c0513428ee6b\"},\"structureFeature\":{\"uuid\":\"a601a801-d753-42b8-8d9c-6a51b356867c\",\"featureId\":\"above ground\",\"structureId\":\"a162493f-4f50-4538-ac56-e01b1e292923\",\"adjustmentRadius\":16,\"facingDirection\":\"FacingDirection.random\",\"grounded\":true,\"unburied\":true,\"blockIntersection\":false,\"blockAllowlist\":[\"minecraft:air\"]},\"featureRule\":{\"uuid\":\"df6d036a-5b0a-4739-8146-c559261e764c\",\"ruleId\":\"planes and Forest\",\"placesFeature\":\"\",\"conditions\":\"{\\\"placement_pass\\\":\\\"final_pass\\\",\\\"minecraft:biome_filter\\\":[{\\\"any_of\\\":[{\\\"test\\\":\\\"has_biome_tag\\\",\\\"operator\\\":\\\"==\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"overworld\\\"}]}]}\",\"distributio