 creating a sense of adventure and mystery. \\n\\nThe area surrounding the tower is lush, with bamboo plants, vibrant green grass, and blooming pink cherry blossoms that add color and contrast to the scene. A warm, inviting glow from a lantern hints at a cozy interior, blending beautifully with the wild yet peaceful surroundings.\\n\\n(This text was generated by Chat GPT)\",\"download\":2231,\"file_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/71a137b3-8073-4c93-8492-0f33b09e3d87.mcstructure\",\"img1_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/snowhaven-tower_2_1731402076.JPG\",\"img2_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/snowhaven-tower_1_1731402076.JPG\",\"img3_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/snowhaven-tower_3_1731402076.JPG\",\"name\":\"Tower House Near Mountain\",\"id\":\"71a137b3-8073-4c93-8492-0f33b09e3d87\",\"premium\":\"false\",\"thumb_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/snowhaven-tower_1_1731402076.JPG\",\"data\":{\"enable\":true,\"chance\":0.75,\"isGrounded\":false,\"isUnburied\":false,\"positionY\":0,\"custom_id\":\"71a137b3-8073-4c93-8492-0f33b09e3d87\"},\"structureFeature\":{\"uuid\":\"a601a801-d753-42b8-8d9c-6a51b356867c\",\"featureId\":\"above ground\",\"structureId\":\"a162493f-4f50-4538-ac56-e01b1e292923\",\"adjustmentRadius\":16,\"facingDirection\":\"FacingDirection.random\",\"grounded\":true,\"unburied\":true,\"blockIntersection\":false,\"blockAllowlist\":[\"minecraft:air\"]},\"featureRule\":{\"uuid\":\"6d6b0854-987e-4dff-88d8-bb7fdceed7b9\",\"ruleId\":\"snow and Frozen\",\"placesFeature\":\"\",\"conditions\":\"{\\\"placement_pass\\\":\\\"final_pass\\\",\\\"minecraft:biome_filter\\\":[{\\\"any_of\\\":[{\\\"test\\\":\\\"has_biome_tag\\\",\\\"operator\\\":\\\"==\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"overworld\\\"}]}]}\",\"distribution\":\"{\\\"iterations\\\":1,\\\"x\\\":{\\\"extent\\\":[0,16],\\\"distribution\\\":\\\"uniform\\\"},\\\"y\\\":\\\"q.heightmap(v.worldx, v.worldz)\\\",\\\"z\\\":{\\\"ext