le, sprawling and grand, boasts a towering central tower that pierces the heavens, a watchful sentinel against the encroaching night.  Jagged battlements crown the walls, hinting at a history of conflict and hardship.  The air around the structure hangs thick with anticipation, a symphony of rustling leaves and the distant chirp of unseen birds broken only by the occasional groan of the wind through the crenellations.  Within its sturdy walls, secrets lie hidden, waiting to be unearthed by those brave enough to venture inside.  Dungeon House 2 is a place of mystery and intrigue, a looming presence that promises both danger and untold wonders. \\n\\n(This text was generated by Gemini)\",\"download\":1528,\"file_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/81da2345-6e1e-401a-9d34-e2206ade10b9.mcstructure\",\"img1_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/1711307598505_1711307608.jpg\",\"img2_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/Dungeon-House-5_1718770777.jpg\",\"img3_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/Dungeon-House-6_1718770777.jpg\",\"name\":\"Dungeon house 2\",\"id\":\"81da2345-6e1e-401a-9d34-e2206ade10b9\",\"premium\":\"false\",\"thumb_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/Dungeon-House-4_1718770776.jpg\",\"data\":{\"enable\":true,\"chance\":0.75,\"isGrounded\":false,\"isUnburied\":false,\"positionY\":0,\"custom_id\":\"81da2345-6e1e-401a-9d34-e2206ade10b9\"},\"structureFeature\":{\"uuid\":\"a601a801-d753-42b8-8d9c-6a51b356867c\",\"featureId\":\"above ground\",\"structureId\":\"a162493f-4f50-4538-ac56-e01b1e292923\",\"adjustmentRadius\":16,\"facingDirection\":\"FacingDirection.random\",\"grounded\":true,\"unburied\":true,\"blockIntersection\":false,\"blockAllowlist\":[\"minecraft:air\"]},\"featureRule\":{\"uuid\":\"6d6b0854-987e-4dff-88d8-bb7fdceed7b9\",\"ruleId\":\"snow and Frozen\",\"placesFeature\":\"\",\"conditions\":\"{\\\"placement_pass\\\":\\\"final_pass\\\",\\\"minecraft:biome_filter\\\":[{\