cture from various angles to provide an expansive view of its design complexity and scale. This castle stands as a testament to the creativity and architectural prowess that players can achieve within the game's block-building environment.\\n\\nThe overall atmosphere conveyed by this image is one of wonder and awe at the sheer volume and detail put into constructing such a monumental Minecraft structure, reflecting not only the player's imagination but also their dedication and time investment in its creation.\",\"download\":4310,\"file_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/8c7a8f05-e041-4e81-8cb7-266c61692ded_1.mcstructure\",\"img1_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/Castle_2_1758181954.jpg\",\"img2_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/Castle_3_1758181954.jpg\",\"img3_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/Castle_1_1758181954.jpg\",\"name\":\"Castle\",\"id\":\"8c7a8f05-e041-4e81-8cb7-266c61692ded\",\"premium\":\"false\",\"thumb_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/Castle_1_1758181954.jpg\",\"data\":{\"enable\":true,\"chance\":0.75,\"isGrounded\":false,\"isUnburied\":false,\"positionY\":0,\"custom_id\":\"8c7a8f05-e041-4e81-8cb7-266c61692ded\"},\"structureFeature\":{\"uuid\":\"a601a801-d753-42b8-8d9c-6a51b356867c\",\"featureId\":\"above ground\",\"structureId\":\"a162493f-4f50-4538-ac56-e01b1e292923\",\"adjustmentRadius\":16,\"facingDirection\":\"FacingDirection.random\",\"grounded\":true,\"unburied\":true,\"blockIntersection\":false,\"blockAllowlist\":[\"minecraft:air\"]},\"featureRule\":{\"uuid\":\"90752137-2398-493a-88be-96b3354552e4\",\"ruleId\":\"planes\",\"placesFeature\":\"\",\"conditions\":\"{\\\"placement_pass\\\":\\\"final_pass\\\",\\\"minecraft:biome_filter\\\":[{\\\"any_of\\\":[{\\\"test\\\":\\\"has_biome_tag\\\",\\\"operator\\\":\\\"==\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"plains\\\"}]}]}\",\"distribution\":\"{\\\"iterations\\\":1,\\\"scatter_chance\\\":{\\\"denominator\\\":300,\\\"numerator\\