57391\",\"ruleId\":\"ocean\",\"placesFeature\":\"\",\"conditions\":\"{\\\"placement_pass\\\":\\\"final_pass\\\",\\\"minecraft:biome_filter\\\":[{\\\"any_of\\\":[{\\\"test\\\":\\\"has_biome_tag\\\",\\\"operator\\\":\\\"==\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"cold_ocean\\\"},{\\\"test\\\":\\\"has_biome_tag\\\",\\\"operator\\\":\\\"==\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"deep_lukewarm_ocean\\\"},{\\\"test\\\":\\\"has_biome_tag\\\",\\\"operator\\\":\\\"==\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"deep_frozen_ocean\\\"},{\\\"test\\\":\\\"has_biome_tag\\\",\\\"operator\\\":\\\"==\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"deep_ocean\\\"},{\\\"test\\\":\\\"has_biome_tag\\\",\\\"operator\\\":\\\"==\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"deep_warm_ocean\\\"},{\\\"test\\\":\\\"has_biome_tag\\\",\\\"operator\\\":\\\"==\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"frozen_ocean\\\"},{\\\"test\\\":\\\"has_biome_tag\\\",\\\"operator\\\":\\\"==\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"ocean\\\"}]}]}\",\"distribution\":\"{\\\"iterations\\\":1,\\\"scatter_chance\\\":{\\\"denominator\\\":1700,\\\"numerator\\\":1},\\\"x\\\":{\\\"distribution\\\":\\\"uniform\\\",\\\"extent\\\":[0,16]},\\\"y\\\":62,\\\"z\\\":{\\\"distribution\\\":\\\"uniform\\\",\\\"extent\\\":[0,16]}}\"}}","display_name":"Structure","group_id":"root","type":"structure","create_time":"2026-04-02T13:22:28.513234"},{"item_id":"db13012e-0cf9-44f7-b1bc-c78b21ee4282","item_name":"Structure","item_icon":"custom/structure.png","item_texture":"","item_skins_dir":"custom/skins/armchairs","item_icons_dir":"custom/icons/armchairs","item_entity_dir":"entities/items/pumpkin.json","item_skin":"","premium":false,"premium_users_only":false,"disable":false,"tag":"structure","itemBuilding":"{\"author\":\"\",\"category\":\"Medieval\",\"desc\":\"Welcome to the Fantasy Medieval Cherry House, an enchanting and whimsical dwelling nestled amidst the picturesque landscape of a virtual world. Designed in the distinctive blocky style synonymous with Minecraft, the cherry house boasts charming architecture that reflects its fantastical nature.\\nThe exterior is adorned with vibrant pink blossoms from cherry trees, which not only add to the aesthetic appeal but also create an inviting atmosphere around the structure. The main building features multiple levels and a variety of windows, giving it a cozy yet expansive feel.\\nUpon closer inspection, you'll notice intricate details such as ivy climbing up walls, wooden beams supporting the roof, and quaint lanterns hanging from various points on the exterior. These elements combine to create an enchanting atmosphere that transports players into a magical realm straight out of medieval fantasy stories.\\n\\nInside, the interior continues with its charming theme. Warm lighting emanates from lamps or torches scattered throughout the rooms, casting soft shadows and creating an intimate ambiance. The furniture is thoughtfully arranged for both functionality and comfort, while decorative items like tapestries on walls add a touch of personality to each space.\\nThe Fantasy Medieval Cherry House serves as more than just a home; it's a testament to creativity and imagination within the virtual world that Minecraft offers its players. Its architecture invites exploration, with hidden passageways or secret doors potentially revealing new adventures for those who dare venture inside.\\n\\nOverall, this structure stands out in the realm of Minecraft creations due to its unique blend of fantasy elements combined with classic medieval design cues. It's a must-visit destination for any fan of building and exploring within virtual landscapes like that found on platforms such as Roblox or Mojang Studios' official servers.\",\"download\":20424,\"file_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/db13012e-0cf9-44f7-b1bc-c78b21ee4282.mcstructure\",\"img1_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/23109_2_1739505483.JPG\",\"img2_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/23109_3_1739505483.JPG\",\"img3_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/23109_4_1739505483.JPG\",\"name\":\"Fantasy Medieval Cherry House\",\"id\":\"db13012e-0cf9-44f7-b1bc-c78b21ee4282\",\"premium\":\"false\",\"thumb_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/23109_1_1739505483.jpg\",\"data\":{\"enable\":true,\"chance\":0.75,\"isGrounded\":false,\"isUnburied\":false,\"positionY\":0,\"custom_id\":\"db13012e-0cf9-44f7-b1bc-c78b21ee4282\"},\"structureFeature\":{\"uuid\":\"a601a801-d753-42b8-8d9c-6a51b356867c\",\"featureId\":\"above ground\",\"structureId\":\"a162493f-4f50-4538-ac56-e01b1e292923\",\"adjustmentRadius\":16,\"facingDirection\":\"FacingDirection.random\",\"grounded\":true,\"unburied\":true,\"blockIntersection\":false,\"blockAllowlist\":[\"minecraft:air\"]},\"featureRule\":{\"uuid\":\"a457d213-ab52-4088-821e-40b1251f3144\",\"ruleId\":\"pink\",\"placesFeature\":\"\",\"conditions\":\"{\\\"placement_pass\\\":\\\"final_pass\\\",\\\"minecraft:biome_filter\\\":[{\\\"any_of\\\":[{\\\"test\\\":\\\"has_biome_tag\\\",\\\"operator\\\":\\\"==\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"cherry_grove\\\"}]}]}\",\"distribution\":\"{\\\"iterations\\\":1,\\\"scatter_chance\\\":{\\\"denominator\\\":200,\\\"numerator\\\":1},\\\"x\\\":{\\\"distribution\\\":\\\"uniform\\\",\\\"extent\\\":[0,16]},\\\"y\\\":\\\"q.heightmap(v.worldx, v.worldz)\\\",\\\"z\\\":{\\\"distribution\\\":\\\"uniform\\\",\\\"extent\\\":[0,16]}}\"}}","display_name":"Structure","group_id":"root","type":"structure","create_time":"2026-04-02T13:22:26.783770"},{"item_id":"db583a7c-c377-47ed-8061-2eeeba7c26c9","item_name":"Structure","item_icon":"custom/structure.png","item_texture":"","item_skins_dir":"custom/skins/armchairs","item_icons_dir":"custom/icons/armchairs","item_entity_dir":"entities/items/pumpkin.json","item_skin":"","premium":false,"premium_users_only":false,"disable":false,"tag":"structure","itemBuilding":"{\"author\":\"\",\"category\":\"Medieval\",\"desc\":\"The \\\"Japanese Cherry\\\" is an intricately designed Minecraft creation, showcasing the beauty and elegance of traditional East Asian architecture within the game's blocky aesthetic. The building features multiple levels connected by wooden beams and pillars, evoking a sense of grandeur and stability.\\nUpon closer inspection, one can observe intricate details such as pink cherry blossom trees lining the front facade, symbolizing life cycles and the transient nature of existence in Japanese culture. A large stone wall with ornate carvings serves as a backdrop to this architectural marvel.\\nThe \\\"Japanese Cherry\\\" boasts numerous windows adorned with colorful banners and hanging lanterns that illuminate its interiors, creating an inviting atmosphere within the game's digital environment. The surrounding area is carefully landscaped, featuring greenery like bamboo plants and well-manicured grass, enhancing the overall harmony between nature and human-made structures in this captivating Minecraft construction.\",\"download\":9148,\"file_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/db583a7c-c377-47ed-8061-2eeeba7c26c9.mcstructure\",\"img1_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/Japanese-Cherry_2_1765526759.jpg\",\"img2_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/Japanese-Cherry_3_1765526759.jpg\",\"img3_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/Japanese-Cherry_1_1765526759.jpg\",\"name\":\"Japanese Cherry\",\"id\":\"db583a7c-c377-47ed-8061-2eeeba7c26c9\",\"premium\":\"false\",\"thumb_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/Japanese-Cherry_1_1765526759.jpg\",\"data\":{\"enable\":true,\"chance\":0.75,\"isGrounded\":false,\"isUnburied\":false,\"positionY\":0,\"custom_id\":\"db583a7c-c377-47ed-8061-2eeeba7c26c9\"},\"structureFeature\":{\"uuid\":\"a601a801-d753-42b8-8d9c-6a51b356867c\",\"featureId\":\"above ground\",\"structureId\":\"a162493f-4f50-4538-ac56-e01b1e292923\",\"adjustmentRadius\":16,\"facingDirection\":\"FacingDirection.random\",\"grounded\":true,\"unburied\":true,\"blockIntersection\":false,\"blockAllowlist\":[\"minecraft:air\"]},\"featureRule\":{\"uuid\":\"a457d213-ab52-4088-821e-40b1251f3144\",\"ruleId\":\"pink\",\"placesFeature\":\"\",\"conditions\":\"{\\\"placement_pass\\\":\\\"final_pass\\\",\\\"minecraft:biome_filter\\\":[{\\\"any_of\\\":[{\\\"test\\\":\\\"has_biome_tag\\\",\\\"operator\\\":\\\"==\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"cherry_grove\\\"}]}]}\",\"distribution\":\"{\\\"iterations\\\":1,\\\"scatter_chance\\\":{\\\"denominator\\\":200,\\\"numerator\\\":1},\\\"x\\\":{\\\"distribution\\\":\\\"uniform\\\",\\\"extent\\\":[0,16]},\\\"y\\\":\\\"q.heightmap(v.worldx, v.worldz)\\\",\\\"z\\\":{\\\"distribution\\\":\\\"uniform\\\",\\\"extent\\\":[0,16]}}\"}}","display_name":"Structure","group_id":"root","type":"structure","create_time":"2026-04-02T13:22:24.652990"},{"item_id":"e793fd64-4329-426a-8fe3-2746bb25e914","item_name":"Structure","item_icon":"custom/structure.png","item_texture":"","item_skins_dir":"custom/skins/armchairs","item_icons_dir":"custom/icons/armchairs","item_entity_dir":"entities/items/pumpkin.json","item_skin":"","premium":false,"premium_users_only":false,"disable":false,"tag":"structure","itemBuilding":"{\"author\":\"\",\"category\":\"House\",\"desc\":\"The Tall Wooden House stood sentinel against the backdrop of rolling hills, a weathered silhouette against the twilight sky. Its narrow frame, constructed of aged, knotty planks, stretched skyward like a ladder to the heavens. A single, sturdy ladder, bolted to its side, provided the only means of ascent, a challenge that both beckoned and intimidated.\\n\\nA second ladder, leaning against the house's front, seemed to offer an easier path. Yet, it was as if the house itself whispered a warning, its silence a testament to the unknown that lay beyond its weathered door. The air hung heavy with the scent of cedar and damp earth, a reminder of the years spent weathering the elements.  The Tall Wooden House, a solitary figure against the vastness of the landscape, held secrets within its rough-hewn walls, a testament to the passage of time and the enduring mystery of the unknown. \\n\\n(This text was generated by Gemini)\",\"download\":621,\"file_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/e793fd64-4329-426a-8fe3-2746bb25e914.mcstructure\",\"img1_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/1723678178249_1723678318.jpg\",\"img2_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/1723678178655_1723678318.jpg\",\"img3_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/1723678178844_1723678318.jpg\",\"name\":\"Tall Wooden House\",\"id\":\"e793fd64-4329-426a-8fe3-2746bb25e914\",\"premium\":\"false\",\"thumb_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/Thumbnail-%2810%29_1727421318.jpg\",\"data\":{\"enable\":true,\"chance\":0.75,\"isGrounded\":false,\"isUnburied\":false,\"positionY\":0,\"custom_id\":\"e793fd64-4329-426a-8fe3-2746bb25e914\"},\"structureFeature\":{\"uuid\":\"a601a801-d753-42b8-8d9c-6a51b356867c\",\"featureId\":\"above ground\",\"structureId\":\"a162493f-4f50-4538-ac56-e01b1e292923\",\"adjustmentRadius\":16,\"facingDirection\":\"FacingDirection.random\",\"grounded\":true,\"unburied\":true,\"blockIntersection\":false,\"blockAllowlist\":[\"minecraft:air\"]},\"featureRule\":{\"uuid\":\"df6d036a-5b0a-4739-8146-c559261e764c\",\"ruleId\":\"planes and Forest\",\"placesFeature\":\"\",\"conditions\":\"{\\\"placement_pass\\\":\\\"final_pass\\\",\\\"minecraft:biome_filter\\\":[{\\\"any_of\\\":[{\\\"test\\\":\\\"has_biome_tag\\\",\\\"operator\\\":\\\"==\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"overworld\\\"}]}]}\",\"distribution\":\"{\\\"iterations\\\":1,\\\"scatter_chance\\\":{\\\"denominator\\\":400,\\\"numerator\\\":1},\\\"x\\\":{\\\"distribution\\\":\\\"uniform\\\",\\\"extent\\\":[0,16]},\\\"y\\\":\\\"q.heightmap(v.worldx, v.worldz)\\\",\\\"z\\\":{\\\"distribution\\\":\\\"uniform\\\",\\\"extent\\\":[0,16]}}\"}}","display_name":"Structure","group_id":"root","type":"structure","create_time":"2026-04-02T13:22:22.799150"},{"item_id":"eb63a80a-a8bb-4ad9-a4df-14bbdd2876cc","item_name":"Structure","item_icon":"custom/structure.png","item_texture":"","item_skins_dir":"custom/skins/armchairs","item_icons_dir":"custom/icons/armchairs","item_entity_dir":"entities/items/pumpkin.json","item_skin":"","premium":false,"premium_users_only":false,"disable":false,"tag":"structure","itemBuilding":"{\"author\":\"\",\"category\":\"House\",\"desc\":\"The Medieval Starter Base is a charming and functional starting point in the popular game of survival, Minecraft. This well-constructed building serves as an ideal beginning exploration hub.\\nThe base features a sturdy foundation made from dark stone blocks that support its walls composed of wooden planks creating a rustic yet inviting atmosphere. A large arched doorway with double doors leads into the interior, providing ample space for players to navigate their way around inside.\\nInside, you'll find various storage chests placed strategically throughout the structure, ensuring valuable resources are easily accessible as your adventure unfolds. Warm lighting from hanging lanterns illuminates the area, casting a cozy glow on wooden beams and supporting pillars that hold up the roof's framework made of layered brown planks.\\nA prominent feature is the chimney atop the building emitting thick smoke against the night sky, suggesting an active fireplace or furnace within. This source of heat adds to the warmth inside while also creating intriguing visuals in-game.\\n\\nOutside, barrels filled with supplies and crates scattered around signify a well-stocked base ready for any challenges that may come your way during gameplay sessions. The Medieval Starter Base is designed not only as a functional living space but also serves as an inspiration for players embarking on their Minecraft journey.\",\"download\":4406,\"file_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/eb63a80a-a8bb-4ad9-a4df-14bbdd2876cc.mcstructure\",\"img1_url\":\"/Addons Maker/house/house_item_1775150497235/Medieval-Starter-Bases_2_1755156840.jpg\",\"img2_url\":\"/Addons Ma